com.palomamobile.android.sdk.messageThread

Class EventMessageThreadUpdated

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.palomamobile.android.sdk.core.qos.BaseJobEvent<JobUpdateMessageThread,MessageThread>
      • com.palomamobile.android.sdk.messageThread.EventMessageThreadUpdated
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEvent<MessageThread>, IJobEvent<JobUpdateMessageThread,MessageThread>

    public class EventMessageThreadUpdated
extends BaseJobEvent<JobUpdateMessageThread,MessageThread>
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) when a messageThread is updated by the client. BaseJobEvent.getSuccess() will return a MessageThread on success, or null on failure
    BaseJobEvent.getFailure() will return a null on success, on failure a non-null throwable.
    To post a messageThread update use IMessageThreadManager.createJobUpdateMessageThread(long, MessageThreadUpdate)
